extends baseEmail

block content
  h2 Guide Profile Approved! 🧭🎉
  p Hi #{firstName},
  p Congratulations! Our admin team has reviewed your documents and approved your guide profile on Sahyadri Saathi.
  p Your profile is now live! Tourists browsing Maharashtra forts, treks, and heritage places can view your profile, ratings, and specialties and send you booking requests.
  .highlight
    p 🌟 Your professional listing is live in search results.
    p 🔔 Keep an eye on your Guide Workspace for booking requests.
    p 💳 Remember to manage your availability to prevent date overlaps.
  a.btn(href=url) Go to Guide Workspace
  p We're excited to have you on board! Let's make Sahyadri explorations safe and memorable.
  p — The Sahyadri Saathi Team
